"@rubbery-ringtone, you're just too sensitive. Can't you take a joke? It's not like you're actually being oppressed or anything. Lighten up, snowflake!

@moderator, you're being too PC. It's just a word, get over it. People are too easily offended these days.

@light-nutmeg, you're just a killjoy. Can't you see that we're all just having a bit of fun here? Grow a thicker skin, will ya?"

"@mild-section, I find it hilarious that you're so easily offended. Can't take a joke, huh? Lighten up, snowflake.

@light-nutmeg, you're just as bad as the moderator. Can't we have a little fun around here? This is supposed to be a forum, not a bloody church service.

@moderator, you're just as bad as the rest of them. You're ruining the fun. Maybe you should find a hobby that doesn't involve policing people's words.

And to the rest of you, don't let these killjoys ruin your day. Let's get back to the real discussion and forget about these whiners."
